      <title>独立游戏程序员生存指南</title>
      <link>http://cn.yjpark.org/blog/2015/02/23/indie-game-developer-survival-guide/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Feb 2015 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>yjpark@gmail.com (YJ Park)</author>
